{"tid":794473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，呢獲我就支持 KFC","createTime":"2018-08-26T09:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T12:34:57.000Z","uid":123335,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b07a037a71bfad1655eb57b7ef983f97d928bc4","tid":794473,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"本身我好鍾意同 FD 去 KFC 食桶餐 <br />\n炸雞配可樂，貪佢既香口又抵食 <br />\n本身都食到上晒癮<br />\n間唔中一定要幫趁一次<br />\n<br />\n但你依家冇膠飲管<br />\n我d 牙齒好易會敏感<br />\n唔飲得kfc d 可樂啦<br />\n<br />\n本身真係好難忍口<br />\n但kfc 個德政實在太好啦<br />\n多謝幫我戒食炸雞  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28f452ccebc4548cce61672f96707f2581c723c","tid":794473,"uid":187108,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1a5bc2e58e46ddc06a26cfe549170fa45fba67","tid":794473,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e28f452ccebc4548cce61672f96707f2581c723c","tid":794473,"uid":187108,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"又係你"},{"pid":"5fd262e518b31cc0e653a9c1a2d3ff2b53a5b73c","tid":794473,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:30:00.000Z","msg":"咁您想食返點搞？"},{"pid":"d86bb5dc48ea04f65a0c26dd647335cca9853ced","tid":794473,"uid":99700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5fd262e518b31cc0e653a9c1a2d3ff2b53a5b73c","tid":794473,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:30:00.000Z","msg":"咁您想食返點搞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:33:10.000Z","msg":"食jollybee"},{"pid":"05e62ae6246a439b7a79502012fd89621b08f694","tid":794